::Grimmler/Rex/Firearm::

Grimmler's eyes widen as he sees a wave of energy heading for him, the 
Maximal diving back, passing out as the wave hits him.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Firearm turns to look at Rex as Battera walks out. "You dolt! She w-" he's 
interrupted as Rex jumps up from his seat.

"Something's registering bigtime on the shields!" Rex says, "One bot, massive 
attack!"

He runs out of a door, gun ready, Firearm following him.
